Template.Name: Decimal
Template.Description: Defines the decimal precision with an parameter. Applies different kinds of rounding

Template.Name: Localization
Template.Description: Formats the number using language dependent formatting (thousand and comma separators).

Template.Name: Sign
Template.Description: Forces a sign before the value

Template.Name: Multiply
Template.Description: Multiplies the value by a given parameter

Template.Name: Time
Template.Description: Formats the given value as a time ISO: HH:MM:SS

Template.Name: Percentage
Template.Description: Multiplies the given value by 100 and adds a percent sign

Template.Name: AbsoluteColor
Template.Description: Colorizes the output based on the sign of the value. The colors are defined in T9 (GUID 140577)

Template.Name: DigitLimit
Template.Description: Shortens values that are larger then a set limit by using short forms: (K = Thousand, M = Million, B = Billion).

Template.Name: Approx
Template.Description: Adds an Approximation prefix to the number

Template.Name: Round
Template.Description: Commonly used short version of Decimals(0, Round, No Reduction).

Template.Name: Duration
Template.Description: Formats the given value as a time duration with up to two most significat units

Template.Name: Text
Template.Description: Text which will not be localized

Standard.Name: A unit that is able to fight

Template.Name: Flock
Template.Description: A group of CFGs move around constantly in a box without asking pathplanner infos

Template.Name: Herd
Template.Description: A Group of Assets is Idling around and running away from danger (e.g. Cities)
